    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/62d4405b78622b347cc14d985f39bd92.poster.avif?t=1752171297\" width=792 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/62d4405b78622b347cc14d985f39bd92.webm?t=1752171297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/62d4405b78622b347cc14d985f39bd92.mp4?t=1752171297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你是堕落王国的国王，曾经是一个强大的统治者，你的王国被背叛所毁灭。现在，你发现自己身处地狱，周围是恶魔实体和邪恶生物，每一天都是生存的斗争。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但你不仅仅想要生存。你寻求一种方法，重返人间，恢复你的王国。收集盟友和有用的物品，同时与敌人的洪流战斗，争取逃脱的机会。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点  </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过100种物品  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的boss战斗  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6个物品/武器槽  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的游戏风格  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速游戏（15-30分钟）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/02f04cc20f7654f1d962a814d95e12ee.poster.avif?t=1752171297\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/02f04cc20f7654f1d962a814d95e12ee.webm?t=1752171297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168060/extras/02f04cc20f7654f1d962a814d95e12ee.mp4?t=1752171297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
